{"tid":513453,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想學陶瓷，亞州仲有邊度有短期課程","createTime":"2017-12-29T14:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T09:58:12.000Z","uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c5851da3544888e56e713ced552819a2bc29836","tid":513453,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:02:12.000Z","msg":"學陶瓷依個念頭一直都有<br />\n但自從開始返工就不了了之<br />\n點知人算不如天算，公司收左皮！加入失業大軍<br />\n但未想搵工住，當休息下去下旅行咁<br />\n<br />\n有睇過上海呀、景德鎮都有陶瓷短期課程<br />\n但想知日、韓或者其他亞洲地區有無d一個月到半年既課程？<br />\n又有無人想一齊去景德鎮學？"},{"pid":"b6911fba358a35d8418bbb52415614a93614043e","tid":513453,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f6e2f2b4dd270e9450c3791500b72504e91a8969","tid":513453,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:08:20.000Z","msg":"日本清水寺附近有"},{"pid":"b40917d4ea92ceaa34cd4cb79bed3b2013823f39","tid":513453,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本清水寺附近有</blockquote><br />\n有睇過，有好多專為外國人面設既<br />\n但都係體驗班，姐係一日個d<br />\n再唔係就一星期一堂，上一個月咁<br />\n但我想搵基礎短期班，一星期上多d咁"},{"pid":"20e5e1eeaab87671cc318a9c9f66c0cf095c266e","tid":513453,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}